            Technique - Développement Rural

abstracts.cdata!:
The project provides, over a three-year
            period, technical assistance and associated equipment to
            plan, prepare, test and begin to implement the following
            subprojects: (a) integrated development of the sterppe zone
            of Ksan Chellala; (b) integrated development of a poor,
            densely populated mountainous region in the daira of Arris
            in the wilaya of Aures; (c) development of an agricultural
            extension service; and (d) assistance to the Banque
            Nationale d'Algerie (BNA) to improve the technical
            capacity of the institution to provide agricultural credit.
